# 🚧 AuraMusic v3.0 — Work in Progress

Yep. We’re already working on **v3.0**.  
This is a **major update** with a complete UI overhaul and deep internal changes.

v3.0 is focused on making AuraMusic feel more modern, consistent, and powerful while improving everything that already exists.

---

## 🎨 UI & Design Changes

- Complete **Material Design–based UI overhaul**
- Migrating to **React Native Paper** for a cleaner and more consistent design system
- New layouts, components, and interactions across the app
- Overall UI is being redesigned from scratch (not just tweaks)

This update changes how AuraMusic looks and feels entirely.

---

## ⚙️ Core Improvements

- **New extraction logic**  
  More reliable, cleaner, and easier to extend going forward.

- **Podcast support added**  
  AuraMusic will no longer be just about music.

- Improvements to all existing features  
  Playback, playlists, downloads, navigation — everything is being refined.

Nothing is being removed, things are being rebuilt better.

---

## 🎯 Goal for v3.0

- Modern Material-style UI
- Better internal architecture
- Easier future feature additions
- More stability and long-term maintainability

This is a big rewrite, so it will take time, but it’s worth it.

---

More details will be shared as development progresses.

